          <span class="cv-skill-label">Marketing : </span>
          <span class="cv-skill-list">SEO, Copywriting, Email Marketing, Analytics</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cv-skill-category">
          <span class="cv-skill-label">Outils : </span>
